notesStmt.note: Although the title page states that it is for 22 & 23 Charles II, the dates given and the imprint date are for the session of 22 Charles II. The contents are for the session of 22 & 23 Charles II, which began 29 Dec. 1670 and ended 22 April 1671.
With a table of the acts on the three leaves following the general title page.
Identified on film as part of Wing E1250 (number cancelled).
Item at 1776:17 imperfect: partial copy, item ends at p. 104.
Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
